{"tid":800172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教大學生會 : 香港獨立才是唯一出路 !","createTime":"2018-08-30T15:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T08:37:55.000Z","uid":28366,"like":194,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"94f20f8c9a84aa090f4c40c80adaf8869d5a0db4","tid":800172,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"【香港獨立才是唯一出路】<br />\n<br />\n一個唔係由香港人真正民選出黎嘅政府，根本就從來無為香港人福祉著想。我地理解到，喺中國統治底下實現普選同民主係無可能，唯有喺中國以外成立一個脫離中國，有主權嘅國家，亦即係香港獨立，先能夠建立一個真正以香港人嘅利益為依歸嘅地方。　<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/235151_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F235151_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a6723cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2018688418197198&amp;id=316480888417968\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2018688418197198%26id%3D316480888417968&d=doj6XsUHDZa6Ii%2FNJf%2FJBU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=974d92a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2018688418197198&amp;id=316480888417968</a>"},{"pid":"291de2975e19a7a16d5e1e71a124797382f87dce","tid":800172,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"睇黎深圳灣單野 就知咩叫土匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1570d3483c7e117a7bd81fb5e7104107b57be4c","tid":800172,"uid":202348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"正皮 上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91a183c9bb46bd75ad17f6d5d46489970a08344","tid":800172,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\